These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, teacher
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, funk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, basketball
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, boat
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the analyst##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | 7up     | lemonade |
| Hobby         | reading  | rock-climbing       |
| Job           | teacher   | analyst    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | romance   |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | metal     |
| Sport         | basketball | soccer      |
| Transport     | boat       | train           |

