.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda
There 2 different types of food: carrot, lemon
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, freelancer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, western
There are 2 different nationalities: british, pakistani
2 different pets are kept: goat, snake
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, bus
1. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
4. the pakistani is on the left of the nurse##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda         | lemonade       |
| Food          | carrot        | lemon |
| Job           | freelancer | nurse    |
| Movie-Genre   | western        | animation  |
| Nationality   | pakistani        | british       |
| Pet           | snake            | goat        |
| Transport     | bus            | motorbike       |

