.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, woodworking
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, fisherman
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, spy
2 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, baseball
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, jet-ski
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the fisherman is on the left or right of the doctor##3
5. the fisherman is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | almond-milk     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | traveling    |
| Job           | fisherman   | doctor |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | spy     |
| Pet           | pony     | chinchilla      |
| Sport         | handball     | baseball     |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | motorbike        |

