.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, rock
2 different pets are kept: horse, cat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, golf
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, ship
1. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | iced-tea   |
| Hobby         | collecting | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts      | spy     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | punk        |
| Pet           | horse        | cat |
| Sport         | climbing    | golf |
| Transport     | ship         | subway       |

