There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, french
2 different pets are kept: pony, cat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, weightlifting
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the french##1
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the quad-bike is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the dutch is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
6. the writer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Job           | accountant    | writer  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror       | martial-arts    |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | r&b       |
| Nationality   | french       | dutch    |
| Pet           | cat           | pony     |
| Sport         | cricket | weightlifting |
| Transport     | skateboard    | quad-bike        |

